quran[70]{c,v,t}:
  69,1,Olunaku olwokwolesa amazima (olunaku lw’enkomerero)
  69,2,Olunaku lwokwolesa amazima kyeki
  69,3,Naye omanyi olunaku olwokwolesa amazima kyeki
  69,4,Abantu ba Thamud n'aba A'adi baalimbisa olunaku olwentiisa
  69,5,Abantu ba Thamud bazikirizibwa nakubwatuka okwamanyi
  69,6,Ate ba A'adi nebazikirizibwa nakibuyaga owamanyi ennyo eyalimu obunyogovu
  69,7,"Gweyabamazaamu ebiro musanvu nenaku munaana awatali kuyimiriramu, walaba abantu nga bagudde eri nga balinga enduli zemitende ezikutuddwako amasanso"
  69,8,Gwe mu kulaba waliwo eyawona
  69,9,"Farawo, n'abamukulembera, naabo abali kubyalo bya Luutu bayonoona"
  69,10,Ekyatuusa buli bamu okujeemera omubaka Katonda gwe yabatumira. Katonda kye yava abakwata olukwata oluyitirivu
  69,11,Aba Nuhu amazzi bwegaabooga okubawonya twabasaabaliza mulyato
  69,12,Olwo nno tulyoke tukibafuulire mmwe ekyokwebuulirira era gakitegeere amatu agategeera
  69,13,Naye engombe bwerifuyibwa olufuuwa olusooka
  69,14,Ensi nensozi birisitulwa nebimementulwa omulundi gumu
  69,15,Olwo nno olunaku lw’enkomerero luliba lutuuse
  69,16,"Eggulu ligenda kweyasaamu, nga ku lunaku olwo ligenda kuba lyabirivu"
  69,17,"Nga ba Malayika bali kumabbali galyo, nga waggulu waabwe kulunaku olwo ba Malayika munaana beebalisitula Arishi y'amukama Katonda wo"
  69,18,Ku lunaku olwo mugenda kuleetebwa mubalibwe tewali kintu kyonna kyemukola kigenda kwekweka
  69,19,Naye oyo alikwasibwa ekitabo kye mu mukono gwe ogwaddyo agenda kugamba nti abange mujje musome ekitabo kyange
  69,20,Mazima nali nkakasa nti ngenda kubalibwa
  69,21,Oyo nno agenda kubeera mu bulamu obwesiimisa
  69,22,Mu jjana ey'a waggulu
  69,23,Ebibala byayo nga birengejjera kumpi
  69,24,Kale mulye era munywe muyogeyoge olwebyo byemwakulembeza mu nnaku ezaayita
  69,25,Naye oyo alikwasibwa ekitabo kye mu mukono gwe ogwa kkono aligamba nti zinsanze singa siwereddwa kitabo kyange
  69,26,Era nessimanya kubalibwa kwange
  69,27,Waakiri singa bwennafa kyekyamala nessizuukira
  69,28,Ebyobugagga byange tebingasizza
  69,29,Sikyalina byakuwoza
  69,30,Mu kiseera ekyo Katonda agenda kulagira nti mumukwate mumulijje
  69,31,Bwemumala mumukasuke mu muliro
  69,32,Bwemumala mumuyiseemu olujegere oluwanvu bwalwo obwenkana emikono nsanvu
  69,33,Anti yali takkiriza Katonda owekitiibwa
  69,34,Era nga takubiriza kuliisa banaku
  69,35,N'olwekyo olwaleero wano talinawo muntu amulumirwa
  69,36,Nga bwatalina kyakulya okugyako masirasira
  69,37,Ebintu ebitayinza kulibwa okugyako abonoonyi
  69,38,Tewali kingana kulayira ebyo byemulaba
  69,39,Nebyo byemutalaba
  69,40,Mazima Kur'ani bigambo bya Katonda byeyassa ku mubaka (Nabbi Muhammad) ow'ekitiibwa
  69,41,Ssi bigambo bya mutontomi naye Iman yammwe yentono
  69,42,Era sibigambo bya mulaguzi naye mufumitiriza kitono (nemutasobola ku byawula)
  69,43,Byassibwa ku ye okuva eri omulezi w'ebitonde
  69,44,Singa yetantala natwogeza ebigambo byetutaamutuma
  69,45,Twalimukutteko n'amanyi
  69,46,Olwo nno netumukutula omusuwa gw'obulamu
  69,47,Era tewali mumwe ayinza kutulemesa kutuukiriza ekyo kuye
  69,48,Mazima yyo Kur'ani kyakwebuulirira eri abatya Katonda
  69,49,Era mazima ddala tumanyi nti mu mmwe mulimu abalimbisa (Kur'ani)
  69,50,Mazima okugirimbisa (Kur'ani) kugenda kubeera kwejjusa kunene eri abakafiiri
  69,51,Mazima yo Kur'ani ge mazima aga namaddala
  69,52,Kale nno tendereza erinnya lya Mukama Katonda wo owekitiibwa
  70,1,"Mu ngeri y'okunyomerera\" omu ku bakafiiri\" yasaba oba ebibonerezo bijja bijje, so nga ate ddala byakujja"
  70,2,Bituuke ku bakafiiri tewali agenda kubigaana kubatuukako
  70,3,Nga biva eri Katonda nnyini madaala agalinya muggulu
  70,4,"Ba Malayika nga ne Jiburilu mwomutwalidde mwebayita nga bolekera eri Katonda, ekibatwalira olunaku lumu lwokka naye nga ate lwenkanankana e myaka e mitwalo etaano (egy'okunsi)"
  70,5,Kale nno gumikiriza olugumikiriza olulungi
  70,6,Mazima bbo balaba ebibonerezo nga biri wala
  70,7,Ate nga ffe tulaba nga biri kumpi
  70,8,Ku lunaku eggulu lwelirikulukuta nga omuzigo omusanuuse
  70,9,Ate ensozi neziba nga pamba asunsuddwa
  70,10,Era tewali wamukwano agenda kubuuza bikwata ku ffa nfe we
  70,11,"Bagenda kuba nga beeraba (naye nga tebayinza kuyambagana). Omwonoonyi olwokwagala okuwona ebibonerezo byolunaku olwo, aliyagala okwenunula nga awaayo abaanabe"
  70,12,Mukyalawe ne mugandawe
  70,13,N'ekika kye ekimukuuma
  70,14,"Nabantu bonna abali munsi, nga ekyo akikola awone ebibonerezo bya Katonda"
  70,15,"Tekigenda kuba nga bwayagala, mazima ayolekedde muliro ogubumbujja"
  70,16,Ogusiriiriza ddala eddiba
  70,17,Gugenda kukowoola buli eyakubayo amabega nakyuka okuva ku mazima
  70,18,"Era nga yakungaanyanga emmali nagitereka \"natagyamu mugabo gugitukuza"